User Stories (Backlog)
Customer

User registration and login
Priority: High | Estimate: 1 day
As a customer, I want to create an account and log in so that my details and orders are saved.

Browse restaurants
Priority: High | Estimate: 2 days
As a customer, I want to browse nearby restaurants so that I can choose where to order food from.

View restaurant menu
Priority: High | Estimate: 1 day
As a customer, I want to view a restaurantâ€™s menu so that I can decide what to order.

Manage shopping cart
Priority: High | Estimate: 1 day
As a customer, I want to add or remove items from my cart so that I can customise my order.

Place an order
Priority: High | Estimate: 2 days
As a customer, I want to place an order so that the restaurant can prepare my food.

Online payment
Priority: High | Estimate: 2 days
As a customer, I want to pay online securely so that my order can be completed without cash.

Track order status
Priority: Medium | Estimate: 2 days
As a customer, I want to track my order so that I know when it is being prepared and delivered.

View order history
Priority: Medium | Estimate: 1 day
As a customer, I want to view my past orders so that I can reorder easily.

Rate and review restaurants
Priority: Low | Estimate: 2 days
As a customer, I want to rate and review restaurants so that other users can benefit from my feedback.

Restaurant

Restaurant account setup
Priority: High | Estimate: 1 day
As a restaurant owner, I want to create an account so that my restaurant can receive orders.

Manage menu items
Priority: High | Estimate: 2 days
As a restaurant owner, I want to update menu items and prices so that customers see accurate information.

Receive new orders
Priority: High | Estimate: 1 day
As a restaurant, I want to receive new orders in real time so that food preparation can begin quickly.

Update order status
Priority: Medium | Estimate: 1 day
As a restaurant, I want to update order status so that customers and drivers know the progress.

Delivery Driver

Driver registration
Priority: Medium | Estimate: 1 day
As a delivery driver, I want to register an account so that I can accept delivery jobs.

Accept delivery orders
Priority: Medium | Estimate: 2 days
As a delivery driver, I want to accept delivery requests so that I can earn income.

Update delivery progress
Priority: Medium | Estimate: 1 day
As a delivery driver, I want to update delivery status so that customers know when their food is arriving.

Admin

Admin login
Priority: High | Estimate: 1 day
As an admin, I want to log in securely so that I can manage the platform.

Manage users
Priority: Medium | Estimate: 2 days
As an admin, I want to manage customer, restaurant, and driver accounts so that the system remains secure.

View basic analytics
Priority: Low | Estimate: 2 days
As an admin, I want to view basic usage analytics so that platform performance can be monitored.
